            <div type="typology">
               <head>Typology (Local)</head>
               <p rend="typology" xml:space="preserve">West (Maghreb) › Tunisia › North Western Tunisia</p>
               <p>Bedouin-type dialect</p>
            </div>
            <div type="general">
               <p xml:space="preserve">About 10 km from the town of Kisra in the governorate of Siliana, il-Garya consists of a few small neighbourhoods, among them il-Garya iš-Šamālīya and il-Garya il-Žanūbīya. This region is known for its beautiful nature, the olive groves and the mountainous landscape. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="researchHistory">
               <p xml:space="preserve">To the best of our knowledge hitherto no research has been done on the dialect of il-Garya, however this dialect is linguistically investigated within the TUNOCENT project.</p>
